author: The Irish Times
title: Coronavirus: Global death toll reaches 150,000, says Reuters tally
description: Total confirmed cases globally reaches 2.1 million, says Johns Hopkins University
content:
The number of deaths worldwide linked to coronavirus reached 150,000 on Friday, according to a Reuters tally.
